vulnerability_findings.name: timestamp
vulnerability_findings.message:
TimedCrowdsale.constructor (IncreasingPriceCrowdsale.sol#486-494) uses timestamp for comparisons
	Dangerous comparisons:
	- require(bool)(openingTime >= block.timestamp) (IncreasingPriceCrowdsale.sol#488)

vulnerability_findings.name: timestamp
vulnerability_findings.message:
TimedCrowdsale.isOpen (IncreasingPriceCrowdsale.sol#512-516) uses timestamp for comparisons
	Dangerous comparisons:
	- block.timestamp >= _openingTime && block.timestamp <= _closingTime (IncreasingPriceCrowdsale.sol#514)

vulnerability_findings.name: timestamp
vulnerability_findings.message:
TimedCrowdsale.hasClosed (IncreasingPriceCrowdsale.sol#521-525) uses timestamp for comparisons
	Dangerous comparisons:
	- block.timestamp > _closingTime (IncreasingPriceCrowdsale.sol#523)
